io.flic.lib

Class FlicBroadcastReceiverFlags

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.flic.lib.FlicBroadcastReceiverFlags

  • public class FlicBroadcastReceiverFlags
extends java.lang.Object
    Used in FlicButton.registerListenForBroadcast(int) to tell which events you want to listen for. If you are concerned about low latencies and performance, only register the flags you actually use. These can be bitwise-or'ed together.
